Integration Package: This is a required field.  This field is a text field and will be compared for an exact match in the system.  If no exact match is found, the row will be marked invalid.  To find the integration package name, refer to the Integration Package field on any Active Property in Property Setup.
Property Code: The Property Code field is an alphanumeric field only and is limited to 10 characters.  This field will be checked for an exact match.  If no exact match exists, the row will be marked invalid.  This is a required field for this upload.  If missing, the row will be marked inactive.
Code: This is a required field. Data should be an alphanumeric only and is limited to 10 characters. if a value is not found, the row should be marked invalid.
Name: This is a required field. Data should be an alphanumeric only and is limited to 50 characters. if a value is not found, the row should be marked invalid.
Type: This is an alphanumeric field that corresponds to a department/unit type name; it should not exceed 255 characters
